    <body>
        <div class="note">
            <p class="Note-Text">The track changes setting is global<MadCap:conditionalText MadCap:conditions="Products.Flare"> in a project</MadCap:conditionalText>. For example, let's say you have two topics open. With focus on topic A, you enable the track changes feature. If you bring focus to topic B, the track changes option is now also enabled for that topic. If you then open other topics after that point, the track changes feature will be enabled in those topics as well.</p>
        </div>
    </body>
</html>